{"tid":332181,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"求救！岩先疏忽俾隻貓吸左啲殺蟲水味！","createTime":"2017-07-22T19:11:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T19:41:55.000Z","uid":65377,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"860203c8d06b7b560fd74101c321c628c47a5138","tid":332181,"uid":65377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T19:11:54.000Z","msg":"我岩先係廳見到隻大蟑螂係地下，一時驚得滯攞左支有除蟲菊既噴霧殺蟲水噴佢（低空噴左好短既一下，而隻貓就係好遠）事關屋企支寵物用殺蟲水岩岩用完。<br />\n<br />\n噴完之後地板即刻好大陣殺蟲水味，唔知道隻貓會唔會聞到（應該都聞到啦，我都聞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）雖然我已經即刻抹地同埋吹風散氣，但硬係仍住仍住陣味仲係到咁。<br />\n<br />\n唔知道貓聞到既話會點？佢一定無掂到殺蟲水，但聞到就應該有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 暫時就無乜事仲好似平時咁<br />\n<br />\n好驚，但又無錢帶佢睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （屋企出左啲事全家人都揹緊債）"},{"pid":"258b3674ee519db92d43232f23ed83cfb3049b70","tid":332181,"uid":5329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T19:34:23.000Z","msg":"唔好咁撚痴線啦好嘛？"},{"pid":"61a843806cb26e9dae833863388bb3b4ee358f19","tid":332181,"uid":6778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T19:37:47.000Z","msg":"比番隻貓人啦"},{"pid":"69515cb609352317ba90259c8223aba9c91f48eb","tid":332181,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T19:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d79db5cd25699db691b8a67dc939176aecc6c69","tid":332181,"uid":64582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T19:41:55.000Z","msg":"驚乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}